                <div class="container d-flex">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 order-lg-1 align-self-lg-center">
                            <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-hero.png" alt="Features that Make Life Easier" class="adaptive-img" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                            <h1>Features that Make Life Easier</h1>
                            <p>The Booking Ninjas bare structure, pre-customization phase, ready for fast use by various sectors.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- /hero -->

            <!-- content -->
            <div class="features-page-grid">
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-1.jpg" alt="Modern APIs and Microservic" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Booking Engine/ Website</h3>
                                        <p>Simple, efficient booking engine system to rapidly place reservations and retrieve guest information. Our Booking Engine system is designed for easy integration with any interface such as a website.</p>
                                        <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_FeatureSpotlight_BE)}" styleClass="button">Learn more</apex:outputLink>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start order-lg-1">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-2.jpg" alt="Reservation Management" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Reservation Management</h3>
                                        <p>Your guests have the booking engine to make their reservations, you have a reservation management system to handle them. This feature helps you collate data, analyze them, store them,  match with existing records and compare, and helps you understand how best to serve your guests.</p>
                                        <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_FeatureSpotlight_AvailabilityGrid)}" styleClass="button">Learn more</apex:outputLink>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-3.jpg" alt="Accounting System" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Accounting System</h3>
                                        <p>An elegant, customizable platform where you can handle all finances related to your business. It integrates with other parts of the system so you don’t need to manually add an entry for new transactions. Built with sophisticated accounting practices in mind, it gives you the best in-house financial management solution in the market.</p>
                                        <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_FeatureSpotlight_AMS)}" styleClass="button">Learn more</apex:outputLink>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start order-lg-2">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-4.jpg" alt="Data Report and Analytics" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Data Report and Analytics</h3>
                                        <p>Won’t you rather have an in-house data system that easily shares data with your other systems? Our Data Report and Analytics feature is built to collect data specifically from within the Booking Ninjas system. So, every reservation, payment, new/old guests, and more is easily reachable from the system, which does the analytics most efficiently.</p>
                                        <a href="#" class="button">Learn more</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-5.jpg" alt="Availability Grid" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Availability Grid (All in One)</h3>
                                        <p>Focusing on two (2) fronts - the staff and the guest. On the staff’s end, the Availability Grid gives you complete oversight of all rooms and reservations in the establishment. You can make remote changes to your rooms’ availability and decide which facility is available to guests.</p>
                                        <p>The guest’s platform gives them the ability to proactively look out for current and future availabilities, giving them the power to plan ahead and takes the middleman out of the process.</p>
                                        <a href="#" class="button">Learn more</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start order-lg-2">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-6.jpg" alt="Room Rate Controller (RRC)" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Room Rate Controller (RRC)</h3>
                                        <p>With AI integration for deep analysis and report generation, Yield Management to help you identify the best revenue sources, and easy reach into your booking engines and channel managers, it’s a dream come true for most administrators.</p>
                                        <p>This allows you to set room rates manually and automatically while sending out mass updates to your booking channels and booking engine. One of the highly coveted features of our system, it gives you absolute control over the present and future of your room rates.</p>
                                        <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_FeatureSpotlight_RRC)}" styleClass="button">Learn more</apex:outputLink>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-page-grid__row">
                    <div class="features-page-grid__cells">
                        <div class="row features-page-grid__cells">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 cell-background"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-page-grid__content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row row-content-height align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-img">
                                        <img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/www.bookingninjas.com/img/feature-core-7.jpg" alt="Communication Services" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="features-page-grid__content-text">
                                        <h3>Communication Services</h3>
                                        <p>Helps you build and maintain good relationships with your guests and staff. The communication service features integrations to efficient tech systems and phone services. It allows for API services (such as Twilio), as well as social media communications channels. It also enables you to integrate your mobile providers (such as Avaya, Cisco, Asterisk, Broadsoft, and Mitel Phone systems)</p>
                                        <p>The entire feature gives you a central platform to handle all your communication needs without having to depend on a third party service.</p>
                                        <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_FeatureSpotlight_CS)}" styleClass="button">Learn more</apex:outputLink>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features-page-text text_center feature-bottom">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Try out our system for free</h2>
                    <apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_Register)}" styleClass="button">Click here to continue</apex:outputLink>
                </div>
            </div>
